  "detailed_description": "<h1>XDesktopSoft COLLECTION</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Software</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About X Music Visualizer</h2>X Music Visualizer is a 3D music visualizer live wallpaper. It can display awesome visualizer when your play music with any player on your Windows.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Support multiple styles of visualizer<br></li><li>Support any music player on your Windows<br></li><li>Support Steam Workshop to Download and Share Visualizer Theme<br></li><li>Low CPU usage<br></li><li>Rich customization options<br></li><li>Support Image and Animate Video Background<br></li><li>Support taskbar transparent</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About X Music Visualizer</h2>X Music Visualizer is a 3D music visualizer live wallpaper. It can display awesome visualizer when your play music with any player on your Windows.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Support multiple styles of visualizer<br></li><li>Support any music player on your Windows<br></li><li>Support Steam Workshop to Download and Share Visualizer Theme<br></li><li>Low CPU usage<br></li><li>Rich customization options<br></li><li>Support Image and Animate Video Background<br></li><li>Support taskbar transparent</li></ul>",
